                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Sefer ha-shorashim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">ספר השרשים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>Includes an appendix on the Aramaic words in the Hebrew Bible. Folio 1 opens with a preface. The epilogue, beginning on folio 300v, precedes the Aramaic section in the manuscript.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>The names of the biblical works referred to in the text are written in the margin in Sefardi cursive.</p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <author>
                        
                        
                        
                        <persName xml:lang="en" key="viaf.org/viaf/100213323">Kimhi, David, 1160-1235</persName>
                        
                        
                        
